node.text:
Thanksgiving looked much different than we had planned. We weren't on the field, but my foundation's team still stepped up for Pittsburgh.  Together we prepared and delivered over 350 meals! These meals were contactlessly delivered to senior citizens in the greater Pittsburgh who were unable to spend time with their families due to COVID. 

The day would not have been possible without my partners and volunteers! Thank you to Ten Four Social, ACORx Pharmacy, and Dive Bar and Grill, Clint K, Canden K, and Kaylen K, Shawn N, Melissa N, Regis N, Jake S, Brian S, Mark R, Kevin P, Mia S, Thomas M, Rob G, Kayla F, Diana O, Amy K, Patty F, Cheryl C, Chris C, Chris N, Sharon K, Kelly W, Alex G, Molly M, Matt K, Lisa T, Rachel M, Dawn G, Nautika T, Sommer T, Christine H, Janet S, Chrisstine H, Tim L, Kimberly S, Tori T, Dan K, Alexa M, Caleb B, Kimberly B, Richard M, Lauren R, Jacque B, Becki O, Jamie B, Brenda N, David O, Kristie M, Jamie S, Scott S, Sarah H, Richard H, Patrick B, Erin K, Steph R, Laurie R, Megan C, Coleen B, Alexa S, Alex V, Rob F, Giavanna S, and John O! @jujufoundation @tenfoursocial @dive_pgh @acorxpharm @mybeautiful_07
